        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «صَوْمُ يَوْمِ اَلتَّرْوِيَةِ كَفَّارَةُ سَنَةٍ وَ يَوْمِ عَرَفَةَ كَفَّارَةُ سَنَتَيْنِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1807 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Fasting on the Day of Tarwiyah is an expiation for one year, and fasting on the Day of Arafah is an expiation for two years.\""
        ]
